"{\"uid\": \"dnaindia.com-viral-photo-gallery-paris-olympics-2024-countries-with-the-most-stylish-uniforms-3098518\", \"text\": \"Sonia Gandhi to contest panchayat elections? BJP plays a trick in Kerala local polls  India slams Pakistan over Sri Lanka aid flight claims: 'Given the urgency...'  Sanchar Saathi: Why are Opposition leaders calling the new app 'Pegasus 2.0'?  BIG breakthrough for India, DRDO successfully tests fighter aircraft escape system, WATCH  'Broke a home to create your own': Did Poonam Kaur take a dig at Samantha Ruth Prabhu? Telugu actress says 'money can buy...'  Air India takes BIG action, suspends officials after finding major noncompliance, here's what we know so far  Has Virat Kohli refused to play in Vijay Hazare Trophy? Here's what online reports claim  GOOD news for EPS-95 members: Minimum pension raised from Rs1,000 to ...  Pakistan sent expiry products as 'relief' packages to flood-hit Sri Lanka? Netizens take jibe says, 'paijaaan..'  Who is Vedamurti Devavrat Mahesh Rekhe? 19-Year-Old Vedic Scholar whom PM Modi praised for...  VIRAL  Shivam Verma|Jul 26, 2024, 11:42 AM IST  1.Team USA  USA is known for it's fashion and preppy outfits. This time, famous fashion brand Ralph Lauren embraced \\\"a patriotic spirit reflected in a signature palette of red, white and blue\\\" for the Paris Olympics 2024.  2.Team Sierra Leone  The official Olympic team kit for Sierra Leone was produced by Adidas in collaboration with the London-based fashion label Labrum.  3.Team Great Britain  The kit for Team Great Britain was produced the brand Ben Sherman, which is returning for the third consecutive year for the outfit.  4.Team Haiti  The vibrant uniforms for team Haiti was created by Haitian-Italian designer Stella Jean to celebrate the country's culture.  5.Team Italy  The Italian athletes will be elegantly attired in Emporio Armani uniforms.\"}"